OL,3,CTwo arrested as fake police allegedly
OL,4,Cdefraud nuns out of #10,000
OL,6,FTwo men have been arrested at
OL,7,FPortsmouth Harbour on suspicion of
OL,8,Fdefrauding a Guernsey convent out of
OL,9,F#10,000.
OL,11,FThey are alleged to have taken the
OL,12,Fmoney from the Order of the Sisters of
OL,13,FMercy on the island by pretending to
OL,14,Fbe police officers who needed the cash
OL,15,Fas part of an investigation.
OL,17,FThe nuns are said to have left the
OL,18,Fmoney in a specific place, which was
OL,19,Fthen collected by the men who had
OL,20,Farrived by ferry.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
