OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1778893392
OL,3,CTwo arrested as fake police allegedly
OL,4,Cdefraud nuns out of #10,000
OL,6,FOfficers from Guernsey tracked them
OL,7,Fthrough CCTV, with Hampshire Police
OL,8,Farresting the duo and recovering the
OL,9,Fcash when they disembarked back in
OL,10,FPortsmouth.
OL,12,FAn urgent appeal has been issued by
OL,13,Fthe authorities, who are concerned
OL,14,Fthat other island organisations may
OL,15,Falso have been targeted.
