OL,3,CTwo arrested as fake police allegedly
OL,4,Cdefraud nuns out of #10,000
OL,6,FAnyone who received a suspicious phone
OL,7,Fcall or other contact from people
OL,8,Fclaiming to be the emergency services,
OL,9,Fparticularly between Tuesday 12 and
OL,10,FFriday 15 May, is asked to immediately
OL,11,Fcall the official Guernsey Police
OL,12,Fforce number 01481 222 222.
OL,14,FMore crime news:
